1
00:01:05,952 --> 00:01:08,384
=No Doubt In Us=
(Adapted from the Manman comic No Doubt in Us)

2
00:01:08,512 --> 00:01:11,424
=Episode 13=

3
00:01:13,359 --> 00:01:16,799
So, you and His Majesty
have switched bodies.

4
00:01:17,280 --> 00:01:19,359
So, the Yu currently in the palace

5
00:01:19,359 --> 00:01:21,239
is actually His Majesty?

6
00:01:21,680 --> 00:01:25,560
I didn't expect you to recognize me
right after using the counter thrust.

7
00:01:26,879 --> 00:01:28,599
It's our family's ancestral martial art.

8
00:01:28,599 --> 00:01:30,599
If you're not my daughter,
how could you do it?

9
00:01:31,319 --> 00:01:34,560
I taught you
how to perform a counter thrust.

10
00:01:35,480 --> 00:01:37,840
Even if you
might have taught His Majesty,

11
00:01:38,319 --> 00:01:42,359
his subtle techniques
couldn't perfectly match yours.

12
00:01:42,760 --> 00:01:45,319
Father, I knew
I couldn't hide it from you.

13
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:49,000
Now you understand
why I had to personally lead the troops.

14
00:01:51,200 --> 00:01:54,799
You have to enter Dada
to get the second volume of the book.

15
00:01:55,359 --> 00:01:57,200
It's to get you and His Majesty
to switch back.

16
00:01:58,239 --> 00:01:58,840
Exactly.

17
00:02:00,280 --> 00:02:02,680
Alright. I can still fight.

18
00:02:02,879 --> 00:02:04,920
We'll advance straight to Dada,

19
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:07,879
retrieve that volume,
and then return home.

20
00:02:08,039 --> 00:02:10,360
Great. If it were anyone else,

21
00:02:10,360 --> 00:02:12,960
they would take the chance
to overthrow the dynasty.

22
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:14,280
Nonsense.

23
00:02:15,479 --> 00:02:17,639
Father, I was joking.

24
00:02:27,639 --> 00:02:30,719
After following me this long,
won't you tell me the truth?

25
00:02:31,439 --> 00:02:32,400
What have you noticed?

26
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:35,960
I care more
about what you can do for me.

27
00:02:37,800 --> 00:02:40,360
I can help you defeat the allied forces
of Dada and Houyi.

28
00:02:41,599 --> 00:02:43,800
Very well. Let's cooperate fully.

29
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:44,960
Help me repel the enemy.

30
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:46,639
And I'll help you reclaim your throne.

31
00:02:47,386 --> 00:02:49,080
(Huna, Queen of Dada)

32
00:02:49,080 --> 00:02:50,039
You knew all along?

33
00:02:51,560 --> 00:02:54,400
Six months ago during a civil strife,
your brother seized your throne.

34
00:02:54,639 --> 00:02:57,800
You thought it was well hidden,
but I knew long ago.

35
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:00,680
But how could you be sure I was Queen?

36
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:03,680
This item only
belongs to Dada's Queen, right?

37
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:05,680
Back in the palace,

38
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:08,439
I reviewed many memorials about Dada.

39
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:10,919
I'm not entirely ignorant about you.

40
00:03:11,479 --> 00:03:13,400
I can help you regain your throne,

41
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:16,080
as long as you pledge eternal peace
between our nations

42
00:03:16,159 --> 00:03:17,960
and recognize Chen
as your suzerain state.

43
00:03:19,759 --> 00:03:23,039
You're no ordinary general.
Who exactly are you?

44
00:03:24,199 --> 00:03:26,879
Xiao Jinyun, the Emperor of Chen.

45
00:03:33,960 --> 00:03:35,759
They say Chen's Emperor is weak.

46
00:03:35,879 --> 00:03:39,800
I never imagined you'd personally fight.
Quite courageous.

47
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:42,879
But

48
00:03:43,599 --> 00:03:45,840
why do you trust someone abandoned
by their own nation?

49
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:48,439
You evaded royal assassins all this way,

50
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:50,400
proving you're not without allies.

51
00:03:51,039 --> 00:03:53,840
I believe you possess the resources
to turn the tide.

52
00:03:54,280 --> 00:03:56,680
And I am your greatest asset.

53
00:03:58,560 --> 00:04:01,199
The alliance of Dada and Houyi
is fundamentally fragile.

54
00:04:01,639 --> 00:04:03,199
My mole in Dada's army

55
00:04:03,199 --> 00:04:05,639
can make Dada and Houyi
turn against each other anytime.

56
00:04:06,199 --> 00:04:08,319
I also know a secret passage
to Dada's royal court.

57
00:04:13,439 --> 00:04:18,319
Xu Yu and Dada's Queen, Tatar Huna,
cooperate to attack Dada's royal court.

58
00:04:18,319 --> 00:04:20,096
(Xu Yu and Dada's Queen, Tatar Huna,
cooperate to attack Dada's royal court.)

59
00:04:22,079 --> 00:04:23,160
The Queen?

60
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:25,759
Xu Yu's move is far too bold.

61
00:04:26,399 --> 00:04:27,360
Jinyun.

62
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:30,040
You're focusing on the wrong thing.

63
00:04:34,240 --> 00:04:35,439
What did I overlook?

64
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:38,639
Jinyun, the key point of this letter

65
00:04:38,639 --> 00:04:41,399
is the Queen of Dada. How old is she?

66
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:44,000
What does she look like?
How does she dress up?

67
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:46,639
How does she speak?
How much meat per meal?

68
00:04:46,720 --> 00:04:48,079
What kind of men does she prefer?

69
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:54,560
Jinyun, if you miss Xu Yu,
just let her know.

70
00:04:55,279 --> 00:04:57,399
Why not write her a letter

71
00:04:57,399 --> 00:04:58,920
and tell her how much you miss her?

72
00:05:05,199 --> 00:05:06,639
Ahan, they've been here.

73
00:05:09,079 --> 00:05:09,579
Yes.

74
00:05:14,519 --> 00:05:17,240
(Abuhun)
Huna, I sent you off.

75
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:19,160
You shouldn't have returned.

76
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:22,439
My father left the throne to me.
Why shouldn't I reclaim it?

77
00:05:22,759 --> 00:05:25,199
Abuhun, you promised my father

78
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:28,680
to guard Dada's borders
and the royal city's peace.

79
00:05:29,199 --> 00:05:30,199
Have you fulfilled it?

80
00:05:30,319 --> 00:05:33,279
But you shouldn't associate
with faithless Chen people.

81
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:34,959
What are you talking about?

82
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:36,839
Faithless?

83
00:05:37,959 --> 00:05:39,600
There must be some misunderstanding.

84
00:05:40,120 --> 00:05:42,480
I'd sooner believe in animals

85
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:44,800
than in the Chen people.

86
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:46,480
What exactly happened?

87
00:05:46,639 --> 00:05:48,839
Days ago, an envoy of Chen was sent,

88
00:05:49,319 --> 00:05:53,000
requesting a truce,
and claiming their Emperor sought peace.

89
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:54,160
I agreed.

90
00:05:54,879 --> 00:05:56,920
Yet they destroyed our rear provisions

91
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:58,279
and slaughtered the escorts.

92
00:05:58,519 --> 00:05:59,399
Impossible.

93
00:05:59,879 --> 00:06:00,720
Chen's Emperor

94
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,959
would never send envoys
to propose a truce.

95
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:04,512
It was a way to divide us.

96
00:06:04,879 --> 00:06:05,639
If you doubt me,

97
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:08,240
I'll have General Xu
show you recent military reports.

98
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:12,920
I trust him.

99
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:17,240
But to convince Dada's warriors,

100
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:19,079
you must surpass him in strength.

101
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:23,079
Compete to hit that military banner.

102
00:06:23,319 --> 00:06:26,480
The loser must accept cooperation.

103
00:06:26,959 --> 00:06:28,480
At this distance, no one can hit it.

104
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:30,100
Let me try.

105
00:06:55,160 --> 00:06:56,879
It was broken.

106
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:17,079
Your Majesty, allow me to greet you
on behalf of my master.

107
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:22,199
We're old friends.
No formalities needed.

108
00:07:22,639 --> 00:07:25,000
(King JiJi)
What will you offer me this time?

109
00:07:26,040 --> 00:07:26,959
Three cities.

110
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:28,279
What?

111
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:31,360
If you keep Xiao Jinyun bogged down
in the desert,

112
00:07:31,519 --> 00:07:33,560
my master will have ample time to usurp.

113
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:36,079
The first thing after seizing the throne

114
00:07:36,279 --> 00:07:39,399
will be giving three cities to you.

115
00:07:39,639 --> 00:07:43,560
He will take the entire Chen,
but will only give me three cities?

116
00:07:44,519 --> 00:07:45,759
That's not enough.

117
00:07:45,759 --> 00:07:46,259
Well...

118
00:07:46,439 --> 00:07:47,319
Your Majesty.

119
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:55,759
Houyi has betrayed us.

120
00:07:55,759 --> 00:07:58,279
They turned on us mid-battle.
Our frontline forces are depleted.

121
00:07:58,279 --> 00:08:00,800
My central army has to split forces
to fight Houyi,

122
00:08:01,319 --> 00:08:03,279
and we're barely holding
against Chen's army.

123
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:06,120
Houyi...

124
00:08:09,319 --> 00:08:10,600
Since Houyi can't be trusted,

125
00:08:10,800 --> 00:08:13,120
why not accept my master's proposal?

126
00:08:13,240 --> 00:08:14,680
Let Chen fall into chaos too.

127
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:18,040
Wouldn't that ease your current crisis?

128
00:08:19,519 --> 00:08:23,040
Abuhun, focus your central army
on resisting Chen's forces.

129
00:08:23,360 --> 00:08:25,759
I'll deploy troops to counter Houyi.

130
00:08:28,319 --> 00:08:31,120
Tell your master
that I'll take the three cities.

131
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:32,720
Yes.

132
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:46,840
Everything proceeds as planned.

133
00:08:46,919 --> 00:08:49,679
The King JiJi sent his royal soldiers
to fight Houyi.

134
00:08:50,080 --> 00:08:52,080
Dada Palace now has minimal guards.

135
00:08:52,399 --> 00:08:52,960
Huna.

136
00:08:53,759 --> 00:08:56,600
We'll enter through the secret passage
to prevent your brother's escape.

137
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:57,100
Okay.

138
00:08:57,840 --> 00:09:00,080
Abuhun, delay the royal forces first.

139
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:01,559
Spare those who surrender.

140
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:03,000
As you command.

141
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:05,879
My foolish brother truly is incompetent.

142
00:09:06,320 --> 00:09:07,559
He fell for it so easily.

143
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:08,879
What a fool.

144
00:09:09,039 --> 00:09:11,919
After Huna reclaims the throne,
you must return immediately.

145
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:14,000
Chen's traitor is about to act.

146
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:16,759
They indeed started a scheme
to divide us.

147
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:18,440
We end this swiftly.

148
00:09:18,639 --> 00:09:19,519
Xu Duo, hear my order!

149
00:09:19,759 --> 00:09:20,259
Yes?

150
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:22,360
After Huna and I enter the royal city,

151
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:24,200
you lead our forces to storm the palace.

152
00:09:24,360 --> 00:09:27,279
We swear to follow Your Majesty
to conquer Dada Palace!

153
00:09:27,879 --> 00:09:31,799
- We swear to conquer Dada Palace!
- We swear to conquer Dada Palace!

154
00:09:32,399 --> 00:09:33,559
All warriors, hear my order!

155
00:09:33,960 --> 00:09:36,240
Advance with me into Dada!

156
00:09:36,759 --> 00:09:37,440
Giddy up!

157
00:09:37,440 --> 00:09:37,940
Giddy up!

158
00:09:38,360 --> 00:09:38,879
Giddy up!

159
00:09:38,879 --> 00:09:39,379
Giddy up!

160
00:09:39,519 --> 00:09:40,600
- Giddy up!
- Giddy up!

161
00:09:40,700 --> 00:09:41,200
Giddy up!

162
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:41,700
Giddy up!

163
00:09:50,679 --> 00:09:52,039
How's my aim?

164
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:52,799
Who's there?

165
00:09:53,879 --> 00:09:54,960
Show yourself!

166
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:56,799
Good shot.

167
00:09:57,200 --> 00:10:01,360
But if you don't shoot my brother,
he won't submit.

168
00:10:14,039 --> 00:10:16,279
I'm here
to discipline my useless brother.

169
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:19,320
Tatar Huna, I showed mercy
for our sibling bond.

170
00:10:19,639 --> 00:10:22,080
I sold you cheap as a dancer
instead of killing you.

171
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:24,120
You'll get yourself killed.

172
00:10:24,720 --> 00:10:26,600
Guards! Help!

173
00:10:26,879 --> 00:10:27,639
No one's coming.

174
00:10:28,240 --> 00:10:31,360
Your loyalists in this city are dead.

175
00:10:32,279 --> 00:10:34,799
They pledge allegiance only to Huna now.

176
00:10:37,639 --> 00:10:40,399
Huna! How dare you collude
with the enemy!

177
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:43,799
As Queen of Dada,
I've forged an alliance with Chen.

178
00:10:44,120 --> 00:10:45,519
No more wars will be waged.

179
00:10:46,159 --> 00:10:48,440
Your reign ends now.

180
00:10:54,840 --> 00:10:57,519
His Majesty sends good news
that King JiJi is dead.

181
00:10:57,759 --> 00:11:00,440
Queen of Dada, Huna,
pledges fealty to Chen

182
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:01,960
and sees Chen as their suzerain state.

183
00:11:02,240 --> 00:11:03,840
His Majesty shall return soon.

184
00:11:05,279 --> 00:11:09,399
- Long live His Majesty!
- Long live His Majesty!

185
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:10,759
Rise, all of you.

186
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:12,720
- Thank you, Your Highness.
- Thank you, Your Highness.

187
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:17,480
(Dada's regime has changed.)

188
00:11:17,600 --> 00:11:20,240
(Xiao Jinyun must know about the plot
to divide the two armies.)

189
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:23,759
(Once he returns safely, we're doomed.)

190
00:11:25,519 --> 00:11:28,480
While His Majesty's triumph
merits celebration,

191
00:11:28,480 --> 00:11:31,200
Your Highness has committed adultery
with Her Majesty

192
00:11:31,200 --> 00:11:35,240
when His Majesty is away.
That's a disgrace!

193
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:36,679
Is that true?

194
00:11:36,919 --> 00:11:39,840
Marquis of Zhenbei!
How dare you talk nonsense!

195
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:43,000
Prince Xiaoyao and Her Majesty
have been intimate.

196
00:11:43,240 --> 00:11:45,240
Such a rumor is already well known
in the palace.

197
00:11:45,240 --> 00:11:46,799
Brothers turn against each other.

198
00:11:46,799 --> 00:11:49,960
Prince Xiaoyao intends to usurp.

199
00:11:49,960 --> 00:11:50,759
Enough!

200
00:11:50,960 --> 00:11:53,600
If it's a rumor,
trace its source immediately.

201
00:11:54,200 --> 00:11:55,360
How dare you

202
00:11:55,360 --> 00:11:57,639
accuse me of baseless charges!

203
00:11:58,159 --> 00:12:00,879
We'll await His Majesty's decision.
Court dismissed.

204
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:04,679
To preserve Chen Empire's reputation,

205
00:12:04,840 --> 00:12:08,120
please punish Her Majesty
and confine her to Fengyi Palace.

206
00:12:10,279 --> 00:12:13,600
Please punish Her Majesty
and confine her to Fengyi Palace.

207
00:12:14,639 --> 00:12:18,840
- Please punish Her Majesty
- Please punish Her Majesty

208
00:12:19,440 --> 00:12:23,720
- and confine her to Fengyi Palace.
- and confine her to Fengyi Palace.

209
00:12:25,799 --> 00:12:27,080
Nice try.

210
00:12:56,480 --> 00:12:58,240
Your Majesty, there's a military report.

211
00:13:00,519 --> 00:13:04,399
You may review any military reports.

212
00:13:05,120 --> 00:13:07,279
It's from His... Her Majesty.

213
00:13:09,720 --> 00:13:10,360
The Empress?

214
00:13:16,440 --> 00:13:17,120
Father?

215
00:13:23,320 --> 00:13:26,440
(Winter snow falls, reminding me
of the frontier's bitter cold.)

216
00:13:27,039 --> 00:13:30,960
(A short letter cannot convey
how much I miss you.)

217
00:13:32,600 --> 00:13:34,080
(Your Majesty fights personally.)

218
00:13:34,759 --> 00:13:36,440
(I'm worried sick)

219
00:13:37,240 --> 00:13:39,720
(that the frontier's harsh weather
may harm your health.)

220
00:13:40,399 --> 00:13:41,679
(May Your Majesty be well.)

221
00:13:42,519 --> 00:13:45,840
(Do not exhaust yourself in battle
and take good care of yourself)

222
00:13:46,240 --> 00:13:47,960
(to reassure your people.)

223
00:13:51,039 --> 00:13:53,679
Xiao Jinyun is so sentimental.

224
00:13:55,866 --> 00:14:00,849
♪Brewing a pot of bygone years♪

225
00:14:01,696 --> 00:14:06,798
♪Chill flame, window shade,
console my grieving soul♪

226
00:14:07,482 --> 00:14:12,026
♪Drunk through lifetimes
with no dreams returned♪

227
00:14:12,666 --> 00:14:16,919
♪If not for letting go, how could I
bear to shatter this dream♪

228
00:14:16,919 --> 00:14:19,360
Xu Yu, why are you slacking off again?

229
00:14:19,960 --> 00:14:22,320
Xiao Jinyun? It's bitterly cold here.

230
00:14:22,440 --> 00:14:24,759
Who took you here?
I'll punish them for this.

231
00:14:26,522 --> 00:14:30,266
♪Hairpins carved
with endless sighs and regrets♪

232
00:14:38,279 --> 00:14:41,120
I guess you must be
missing your Empress.

233
00:14:41,600 --> 00:14:44,039
In Dada, whether men or women,

234
00:14:44,240 --> 00:14:46,480
when they're in love,
they show it openly.

235
00:14:47,240 --> 00:14:50,440
You love your Empress.
Others should envy that.

236
00:14:51,120 --> 00:14:53,399
So there's no need to hide it.

237
00:14:54,240 --> 00:14:54,960
Exactly.

238
00:14:55,360 --> 00:14:58,039
In this regard,
I should learn from your customs.

239
00:14:59,679 --> 00:15:03,679
Royal marriages
are rarely matters of choice.

240
00:15:03,919 --> 00:15:05,960
I was even betrayed by my own brother.

241
00:15:06,480 --> 00:15:09,039
To find true love as you have

242
00:15:11,559 --> 00:15:12,960
is a hope I've abandoned.

243
00:15:13,559 --> 00:15:16,200
That's because Dada
has no woman like you.

244
00:15:16,440 --> 00:15:18,279
I believe none deserves you.

245
00:15:19,840 --> 00:15:20,399
Really?

246
00:15:20,919 --> 00:15:21,480
Of course.

247
00:15:23,639 --> 00:15:25,120
Come on, let's drink.

248
00:15:27,279 --> 00:15:27,779
Come on.

249
00:15:56,879 --> 00:15:58,399
Are you attempting a coup?

250
00:15:58,879 --> 00:16:00,679
How dare you use baseless accusations

251
00:16:00,679 --> 00:16:02,679
to target Prince Xiaoyao
and the Empress?

252
00:16:03,320 --> 00:16:06,039
Her Majesty held secret talks
with His Highness in the garden.

253
00:16:06,399 --> 00:16:10,799
She also accompanied him intimately
while he read memorials in the study.

254
00:16:11,080 --> 00:16:13,480
Many witnesses can attest to this.

255
00:16:16,000 --> 00:16:18,960
If they secretly talked,
how would you know?

256
00:16:19,639 --> 00:16:22,039
Have you planted spies in the palace

257
00:16:22,039 --> 00:16:23,799
to surveil His Highness and me?

258
00:16:24,600 --> 00:16:27,320
I wouldn't dare surveil Her Majesty
and His Highness.

259
00:16:27,639 --> 00:16:29,360
So, you admit planting spies

260
00:16:29,919 --> 00:16:32,000
to watch His Majesty's every move?

261
00:16:48,442 --> 00:16:53,626
♪Parting clouds
to pluck the waxing moon♪

262
00:16:54,362 --> 00:16:58,925
♪Brewing a pot of bygone years♪

263
00:17:00,250 --> 00:17:05,665
♪Chill flame, window shade,
console my grieving soul♪

264
00:17:06,234 --> 00:17:10,778
♪Drunk through lifetimes
with no dreams returned♪

265
00:17:11,418 --> 00:17:16,682
♪If not for letting go, how could I
bear to shatter this dream♪

266
00:17:17,050 --> 00:17:22,727
♪Returning to drift
through the mortal world♪

267
00:17:23,066 --> 00:17:25,082
♪Like her, like me, like you♪

268
00:17:25,274 --> 00:17:29,018
♪Hairpins carved
with endless sighs and regrets♪

269
00:17:29,594 --> 00:17:34,266
♪Fate laid bare my deepest thoughts♪

270
00:17:34,810 --> 00:17:36,570
♪Like vows, like remorse, like love♪

271
00:17:36,890 --> 00:17:40,506
♪Loving, hurting,
and regretting our late meeting♪

272
00:17:40,753 --> 00:17:46,280
♪Tell me, after all this entanglement,
who regrets it more♪
